These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, goldfish, chinchilla, horse
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda, water, almond-milk
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, colonial, ranch-style
There are 4 different nationalities: american, italian, malaysian, chinese
 1. the farmhouse house is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8
 2. the american is not to the left of the american##8
 3. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the gothic-revival house is not to the left of the ranch-style house##8
 5. the american is not to the right of the american##8
 6. the person drinking water is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is between the italian and the farmhouse house##2
 9. the chinese is the person drinking water##1
10. the chinese is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
12. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
13. the person drinking water is not to the left of the chinese##8
14. the owner of the goldfish is the malaysian##1
15. the owner of the goldfish is not the farmhouse house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Pet         | turtle     | goldfish   | horse | chinchilla |
| Beverage   | mirinda | almond-milk   | sprite   | water  |
| House         | farmhouse  | colonial  | ranch-style  | gothic-revival |
| Nationality     | american    | malaysian | italian     | chinese    |

