.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, dancing, drawing, fishing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, sailing, cycling, surfing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, november, august, february
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, balloon-flower, azalea, lily
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 2. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##8
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the right of the person who growslily##8
 5. the person who growsdaisy is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##8
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
 7. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
 8. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
11. the person who growsdaisy is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
13. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
14. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
15. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
17. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8
18. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##8
19. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
