 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
10. the person who likes green is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is not to the left of the person traveling to london##8
12. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3

.:: Answer ::.
