4 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, cape-cod, scrabble
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, argentine, colombian, american
 1. the craftsman house is not the person playing monopoly##6
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 3. the fan of metal is the person playing cape-cod##1
 4. the fan of punk is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing snooker##2
 5. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the thai##3
 6. the thai is not to the right of the fan of punk##8
 7. the modern house is in an odd position##4
 8. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5
 9. the modern house is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person playing snooker is the thai##1
11. the argentine is not to the right of the fan of house##8
12. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the argentine##3
13. the craftsman house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
14. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the argentine##3
15. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
