 3. the siglo-smoker is not the person who's birthday is in march##6
 4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 5. the person eating cauliflower is not to the right of the person who growslily##8
 6. the baccarat-smoker is not to the right of the person eating cauliflower##8
 7. the siglo-smoker is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
 8. the person who growsbellflower is the person eating cucumber##1
 9. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
10. the person eating peas is not to the left of the person eating cauliflower##8
11. the vegafina-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person eating cucumber##2
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
13. the person who growsbellflower is not to the right of the person eating cucumber##8
14. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3

.:: Answer ::.
