The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, classical, salsa, jazz
 1. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
 2. the fan of gospel is not the person playing bridge##6
 3. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
 4. the person who likes ebony is the owner of the goat##1
 5. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
 6. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the owner of the goldfish##7
 7. the fan of jazz is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
 8. the fan of classical is somewhere between the person playing chess and the person playing mah-jongg##7
 9. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who likes blue is not to the left of the person who likes blue##8
11. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left##1
12. the person who likes black is on the far right##1
13. the fan of jazz is the person playing chess##1
14. the person playing chess is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
15. the fan of classical is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
16. the person who likes blue is not to the left of the person playing billiard##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4       |
