12. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
13. the montecristo-smoker is not to the left of the person playing bridge##8
14. the person playing canasta is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
15. the person playing canasta is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
16. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Game           | mah-jongg | canasta       | bridge      | domino  |
| City   | berlin    | edinburgh | marseilles   | boston   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | fanta          | coffee      | mirinda  |
| Cigar   | bolivar   | chaman      | bluemaster | montecristo |

